{
  "stem": "14613.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too much, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Politically, as I said, we were maybe still too young to-- to discuss or understand it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our life before the war-- at least in my circle-- was a carefree life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I look back on it, maybe it was the best year of my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although, we did feel a certain anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were aware of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were aware of it very often when we went to our school, to the Jewish gymnasium, and we had to pass by the Polish schools, the public schools, where the gentile boys used to call us name-- names, and sometimes throw stones at us.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were aware of it that during many holidays, there were problem against Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were aware that there was discrimination in universities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But somehow, we took them as the facts of life at that point.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, to a point, I was aware of the prejudices.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And yet, the few gentiles that we did know-- that my father did business-- they were extremely-- extremely devoted individually to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe one of the best example is that, way after the war-- when I went back to Poland-- some people knew me there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to find the super from our factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I did find him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he came to meet me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think from certain points of view, he knew my father better than I, because he was a grown-up and my father was a grown-up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told me the story, to me and to my wife, that-- and he referred to my father as Mr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Still, the respect was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he would say-- he was a very unusual person.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was-- he said he was a rich man, I was a poor man.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
